{"tid":2328130,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ASUS RT-AC68U touter及AiCloud問題","createTime":"2020-12-16T11:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T10:19:46.000Z","uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31ea64dfc2708126b7baab8f4913f077bdb4dd8f","tid":2328130,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"朋友用ASUS RT-AC68U touter,佢屋企仲有一部HiMedia Q4 pro TV set top box<br />\nrouter同Himedia都分別插咗一部USB HDD<br />\n朋友config好AiCloud,俾咗絛link及login/password我 <br />\nhttps://&lt;name&gt;.asuscomm.com<br />\n我響自己屋企部win 10,用browser,RT-AC68U同Himedia既USB HDD都可以見到,但我地係想<br />\nmap個network drive eg<br />\nnet use z: https://&lt;name&gt;.asuscomm.com /user:username password /persistent:No<br />\n但點都唔得,改成<br />\nnet use z: https://&lt;name&gt;.asuscomm.com/RT-AC68U/&lt;usb drive name&gt; /user:username password /persistent:No<br />\n都唔得,係browser先得,有冇人知點解同可以點set aicloud去做到? thx"},{"pid":"ad51006e8a1c8d23d157b176fef2fbb67fa8457e","tid":2328130,"uid":367723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"叫佢開個vpn畀你再入internal ip 試吓"},{"pid":"14f9e7d1e27317633164676a39eda84e0f76a6ad","tid":2328130,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"AiCloud port用8082, 443要開o左<br />\n<br />\n唔好連https, 直接連 &lt;name&gt;.asuscomm.com:8082 試試"},{"pid":"3252cdc3a5513e80f33f51f0051e45916376db29","tid":2328130,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad51006e8a1c8d23d157b176fef2fbb67fa8457e","tid":2328130,"uid":367723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"叫佢開個vpn畀你再入internal ip 試吓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:46:52.000Z","msg":"結果一樣,browser得,network drive唔得"},{"pid":"cfd7b305b9bb323c60b412f6883a4746cfcd10bf","tid":2328130,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14f9e7d1e27317633164676a39eda84e0f76a6ad","tid":2328130,"uid":17738,"li